        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Considered as unfinished business. (consideration: CR H1532-1533)",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-09",
        "actionTime": "13:07:04",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on S.J. Res. 28, the Chair put the question on passage of the joint resolution and by voice vote, announced that the ayes had prevailed. Mr. Hill (AR) demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H35000",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-09",
        "actionTime": "13:06:25",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "The previous question was ordered pursuant to the rule.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-09",
        "actionTime": "12:24:44",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on S.J. Res. 28.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-09",
        "actionTime": "12:24:24",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rule provides for consideration of S.J. Res. 18, S.J. Res. 28, H.R. 1526 and H.R. 22. The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 22, H.R. 1526, S.J. Res. 18, and S.J. Res. 28 under a closed rule. The resolution provides for one hour of debate on each measure and one motion to recommit on H.R. 22 and H.R. 1526, and one motion to commit on S.J. Res. 18 and S.J. Res. 28.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H30000",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-09",
        "actionTime": "12:24:19",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Considered under the provisions of rule H. Res. 294. (consideration: CR H1514-1519)",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H1L210",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-07",
        "actionTime": "19:20:40",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rules Committee Resolution H. Res. 294 Reported to House. Rule provides for consideration of S.J. Res. 18, S.J. Res. 28, H.R. 1526 and H.R. 22. The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 22, H.R. 1526, S.J. Res. 18, and S.J. Res. 28 under a closed rule. The resolution provides for one hour of debate on each measure and one motion to recommit on H.R. 22 and H.R. 1526, and one motion to commit on S.J. Res. 18 and S.J. Res. 28.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H1L220",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-01",
        "actionTime": "14:16:01",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rule H. Res. 282 failed passage of House.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H1L210",
        "actionDate": "2025-04-01",
        "actionTime": "10:03:16",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rules Committee Resolution H. Res. 282 Reported to House. Rule provides for consideration of H.R. 22, H.R. 1526, S.J. Res. 18 and S.J. Res. 28. The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 22, H.R. 1526, S.J. Res. 18, and S.J. Res. 28 under a closed rule. The resolution provides for one hour of debate on each measure and one motion to recommit on H.R. 22 and H.R. 1526, and one motion to commit on S.J. Res. 18 and S.J. Res. 28. The resolution also provides that H. Res. 23 and H. Res. 164 are laid on the table.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
